      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SELEC    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL'1'       WKGET
      *
     CSR         ESELEC    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #CLR      BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETON                     71
     C                     WRITESFLCTL
